# LearningHub Copilot Instructions

## Project Overview
A React + TypeScript frontend system design learning application built with Vite, MUI, and React Router. The project follows a structured, scalable architecture with clear separation of concerns.

## Technology Stack
- **Frontend Framework**: React 19.2.4
- **UI Library**: Material-UI (MUI) v9.0.0
- **Routing**: React Router DOM v7.14.1
- **Styling**: Emotion (via MUI) + MUI Theme System
- **Build Tool**: Vite v8.0.4
- **Language**: TypeScript ~6.0.2
- **Compiler Plugin**: React Compiler (Babel)

